            proc list_append from ListOps with adaptations, adapt
            proc consume_statement_end with parser

            Let after be proc memory_get_int64 from Layout with parser, 8
            If after is equal to before:
                proc advance_token with parser
            End If
        End While
    Otherwise:
        proc consume_statement_end with parser
    End If

    Return node
End Process

@Reasoning:
Consumes a single optional visibility keyword (public/private/protected) when
present, used inside trait 'as' adaptations where an alias may be reintroduced
with a new visibility. No-op otherwise.
@End Reasoning
Process called "skip_optional_visibility" takes parser as Integer returns Integer:
