@Reasoning:
Top-level function declaration: 'function [&] name (params) [: returnType]
{ body }'. The by-ref '&' marks return-by-reference. Attributes are supplied by
the caller.
@End Reasoning
Process called "parse_function" takes parser as Integer, attrs as Integer returns Integer:
    Note: Parse a top-level function declaration

    proc advance_token with parser            Note: 'function'

    Let node be proc create_ast_node with "function"
    proc set_ast_attribute with node, "attributes", attrs

